data.description: Charming 2BR, 1BA cottage in Bristol. Nicely situated in a great location that's convenient to schools, shopping, dining and more. This sweet home is perfect for first time home buyers or as investment property. Cute front porch is warm and inviting. Kitchen has pretty laminate hardwood flooring, updated sink and faucet and nice subway tile backsplash. Bath has stackable washer and dryer and a new sink. Back yard is fully fenced in with a privacy fence. Unfinished area in basement is ideal for storing mowers and lawn equipment. Leaf guards installed on gutters. Seller to offer a credit toward closing costs for renovations with an acceptable offer. Call today for your private or virtual showing. All information taken from various sources and deemed reliable. Buyer / Agent to verify.
